h football and lacrosse his speed afoot and his passing accuracy won him the starting job as the junior varsity and later varsity quarterback as the varsity quarterback he led the city knights to two undefeated seasons and successive maryland scholastic association aconference championships in  and  as a student schmoke was a member of the baltimore city college acourse a college preparatory curriculum that required him to take latin and other advanced studies not offered to the average baltimore high school student schmoke was elected president of the schools student government in his senior year but also worked in the baltimore community with disadvantaged youth compulsory community service had not yet been mandated for baltimore high school students yet he tutored and mentored young men from the inner city as a member of the lancers boys club college and graduate schooledit schmoke entered yale university in the fall of  he played quarterback on the freshman team that year while at yale schmoke and his classmates started a day care center on campus for the children of the universitys janitors and cafeteria workers who lived in new haven the center was named after calvin hill a former yale football star who became a star running back for the dallas cowboys and still stands today schmoke has been acknowledged as the undergraduate student leader who helped quell the possibility of riot on the yale campus in the wake of the new haven black panther trials in the spring of  as new haven filled with radical protesters yale students demanded the suspension of classes a bitterly divided faculty met to discuss strategy and invited a student leader to address the gathering schmoke who was secretary of the class of  and a leader of the black student alliance at yale was selected to represent the students he spoke only a few sentences the students on this campus are confused theyre frightened they dont know what to think you are older than we are and are more experienced we want guidance from you moral leadership on behalf of my fellow students i beg you to give it to us this moment is credited with helping to dispel the growing tensions the university voted to bend its rules making classes voluntarily optional to the end of the term and despite small outbreaks of violence no campuswide unrest resulted after graduating from yale with a degree in history in  schmoke studied as a rhodes scholar at oxford university and graduated from harvard law school in  schmoke was selected with five other distinguished former collegiate studentathletes for a silver anniversary award by the ncaa in  early careeredit after graduating from harvard law school schmoke joined the baltimore law firm of piper and marbury in  he was selected to be part of the white house domestic policy staff during the carter administration to work in the department of transportation however after only one year working in president carters administration schmoke returned to baltimore to serve as the assistant united states attorney a position he held from  to  elective officeedit schmoke and curt anderson in  as they both launch their political careers in  schmoke ran for his first elected office he challenged incumbent baltimore city states attorney william a swisher in a citywide contest swisher had won the job away from milton b allen baltimores first african american states attorney schmoke ran an energetic grassroots and raceneutral campaign and upset swisher in a landslide on november   he was elected mayor as mayor he became known for his opposition to the war on drugs and his stance in favor of drug decriminalization schmoke initiated programs in housing education public health and economic development during his three terms in office schmoke faced very serious challenges including poor quality schools drug addiction and violent crime some of his controversial positions included advocating the decriminalization of drug use and employing nation of islam security guards in a housing project his achievements included improving the environment of lowincome housing projects a needleexchange program for addicts keeping the tax rate stable and attracting the ravens football team to baltimore in  president george h w bush awarded him the national literacy award for his efforts to promote adult literacy and in  president bill clinton cited baltimores programs to improve public housing and enhance community economic development and named baltimore one of six cities to receive empowerment zone designation in  schmoke served as a committee member for the rudy bruner award for urban excellence after serving three terms as city mayor schmoke opted not to run for reelection in  advocacy for school choice and school vouchersedit in  schmoke delivered some remarks on the subject of school choice and school vouchers at a manhattan institute luncheon in new york an edited version of a transcript of that speech entitled why school vouchers can help innercity children is available online and in that brief web page schmoke explains why he believes that school choice and vouchers will improve the quality of public education for america’s youth particularly innercity minority children schmoke first came out in support of school choice in a speech at johns hopkins university in march  life after politicsedit after leaving office in december  schmoke practiced law at the firm of wilmer cutler  pickering in baltimore in  schmoke was appointed the dean of the howard university school of law in washington dc in  schmoke was appointed an honorary fellow of balliol college oxford he is also on the board of global rights and a member of the christian and missionary alliance in  schmoke delivered the keynote lecture “a new hundred years war the compelling need to reform national drug control policy” for the edward bouchet conference on diversity in graduate education at yale university he also appeared in two  episodes of the acclaimed hbo series the wire the episodes entitled middle ground and mission accomplished featured schmoke in a bit part as a health commissioner he acts as an advisor to the fictional mayor after a rogue police major has legalized drugs in a portion of the city this is a reference to his own feelings on the drug war in july  kurt schmoke became the acting senior vice president of academic matters at howard university a position that in effect made schmoke provost for the university schmoke continued as dean of the howard university school of law it had been rumored he would be named the new president schmoke also taught election law as a seminar class every fall semester to third year law students in january  schmoke was seen holding an umbrella for illinois senate designee roland burris during an outdoor press conference concerning burris seating controversy schmoke was part of the legal team advising burris during the controversy schmoke was appointed vice president and general counsel of howard university in july  on may   the university of baltimore announced that schmoke would become its new president referencesedit  yam november  – powerful persuader  schmoke kurt l on the calvin hill day care center retrieved  april    powerful persuader in the yale alumni magazine november   mayday at yale a case study in student radicalism john taft westview press   biographies  baltimore city history of mayors  kurt l schmoke msamarylandgov retrieved    weavers vision starts it all baltimore sun september   retrieved january   dead link  schmoke kurt l –  blackpastorg retrieved january     welcome to empower baltimore wwwebmcorg retrieved    rudy bruner award for urban excellence selection committees bruner foundation retrieved  january    janofsky michael february   baltimore leaders sour on entire mayoral field the new york times archived from the original on november   retrieved april   cs maint bot originalurl status unknown link  a b why school vouchers can help innercity children  archived from the original on march   retrieved march   i  believe that the democratic party should reevaluate its position on school choice issues  some say that school choice is elitist or even racist the truth is that black lowincome children are among the prime victims of the nation’s failing public schools africanamerican parents know this all too well this is why they have been so open to the idea of school choice   kram mark tom pendergast kurt schmoke biography – started strong wise beyond his years a successful lawyer strong start as mayor of baltimore net industries retrieved april     david simon george p pelecanos  middle ground the wire season  episode  hbo   episode guide – episode  middle ground hbo  retrieved august     david simon ed burns  mission accomplished the wire season  episode  hbo   episode guide – episode  mission accomplished hbo  retrieved august     margaret talbot  stealing life the new yorker retrieved october     office of the provost and chief academic officer provosthowardedu retrieved    schmoke offers aid to us senate nominee burris wjztv baltimore january   retrieved january     kurt schmoke forbes retrieved april     news releases ubaltedu retrieved april    kurt schmoke baltimores first black mayor new honorary fellows at balliol external linksedit kurt schmoke on imdb political offices preceded by clarence du burns mayor of baltimore – succeeded by martin j omalley preceded by william a swisher states attorney baltimore city – succeeded by stuart o simms v t e mayors of baltimore calhoun t smith johnson stiles johnson montgomery johnson montgomery small steuart hunt s smith leakin brady hillen law davies stansbury jerome hollins hinks swann brown blackburn chapman banks van sant latrobe kane latrobe whyte latrobe hodges latrobe davidson latrobe hooper malster hayes mclane timanus mahool preston broening jackson broening jackson mckeldin dalesandro jr grady goodman mckeldin dalesandro iii schaefer burns schmoke omalley dixon rawlingsblake pugh